rtyear=2020|id=16157-4005-1|accessdate=March 6, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|artist=The Weeknd|title=Blinding Lights|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| December 6, 2019\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| {{hlist|[[XO (record label)|XO]]|[[Republic Records|Republic]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://hiphop-n-more.com/2019/11/the-weeknd-to-release-2-new-singles-blinding-lights-heartless-this-week/|title=The Weeknd to Release 2 New Singles 'Blinding Lights' & 'Heartless' This Week|website=Hiphop-n-more|accessdate=December 2, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| December 13, 2019\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| [[Universal Music Group|Universal]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/the-weeknd-blinding-lights-190109-13-12-2019-radiodate/|title=Blinding Lights THE WEEKND|website=Radio Date|accessdate=December 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United Kingdom\n| December 20, 2019\n| rowspan=\"5\"| {{hlist|XO|Republic}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/3tqPdBWF9yMbTrfjWvfKV8t/radio-1-playlist|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220184733/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/3tqPdBWF9yMbTrfjWvfKV8t/radio-1-playlist|archivedate=December 20, 2019|title= Radio 1 Playlist|website=[[BBC]]|accessdate=December 20, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"|United States\n|January 6, 2020\n|[[Hot adult contemporary|Hot adult contemporary radio]]\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=Hot Modern AC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106161725/https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-relea