outers, Enzo}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Belgian male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{Belgium-cycling-bio-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Enzo Wouters\n| image          = Antoing - Triptyque des Monts et Ch\u00e2teaux, \u00e9tape 1, 3 avril 2015, d\u00e9part (C072).JPG\n| image_size     =\n| caption        = Wouters in 2015.\n| fullname       = Enzo Wouters\n| nickname       =\n| birth_date     = {{bda|1996|3|21|df=y}}\n| birth_place    =\n| height         = 1.83 m\n| weight         =\n| currentteam    = {{ct|LTS}}\n| discipline     = Road\n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      =\n| amateuryears1  = 2015\u20132016\n| amateurteam1   = Lotto\u2013Soudal U23\n| amateuryears2  =\n| amateurteam2   =\n| proyears1      = 2017\u2013\n| proteam1       = {{ct|LTS|2017}}\n| proyears2      =\n| proteam2       =\n| majorwins      =\n| medaltemplates =\n| show-medals    =\n}}\n'''Enzo Wouters''' (born 21 March 1996) is a Belgian cyclist, who currently rides for [[UCI WorldTeam]] {{ct|LTS}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.directvelo.com/equipe/1048/lotto-soudal#riders-2019|title=Lotto-Soudal|language=French|work=Directvelo|publisher=Association Le Peloton|accessdate=3 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Major results==\n{{div col}}\n;2013\n: 1st Stage 3 Ober\u00f6sterreich Juniorenrundfahrt\n;2014\n: 1st [[File:MaillotB\u00e9lgica.PNG|20px]] [[Belgian National Road Race Championships|Road race]], National Junior Road Championships\n: 1st Stage 3 Tour d'Istrie\n: 1st Stage 3 Ober\u00f6sterreich Juniorenrundfahrt\n: 1st Stage 3 Internationale Niedersachsen-Rundfahrt\n: 2nd Overall Keizer der Juniores\n::1st Stages 1 & 2b\n: 3rd [[Paris\u2013Roubaix Juniors]]\n;2016\n: 2nd [[Belgian National Road Race Championships|Road race]], National Under\u201323 Road Championships\n: 2nd [[Antwerpse Havenpijl]]\n: 2nd [[Memorial Philippe Van Coningsloo]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{